title: stephen chinner
text:
Fantastic service, fantastic product, fantastic delivery. Really pleasing to deal with a company that understands customers. Since my original two orders were received, I have already placed further orders. I wonder if these guys would be interested in taking over Telstra, or better still, our government.lol. Highly recommend.
Stephen
